'''Belegor''' (born {{FA|340}}) was a man of the [[House of Bëor]].

== History ==
Belegor was the second son of [[Boron]], and the younger brother of [[Boromir (Lord of Ladros)|Boromir]]. He could trace his ancestry directly to [[Bëor]], who was his great-grandfather.<ref>{{WJ|14}}, ''(i) The House of Bëor'', pp. 230-1</ref>

